										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">转眼的功夫就到年底了，</span><strong style="color: blue;">打扫卫生</strong><span style="color: green;">、</span><strong style="color: blue;">备年货</strong><span style="color: green;">，</span><strong style="color: blue;">红红火火迎新年</strong><span style="color: green;">。不过需要提醒大家一下，</span><strong style="color: blue;">备大鱼大肉、干果蔬菜的时候，水果可别忘记</strong><span style="color: green;">。</span></p>
<p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">水果</span></strong>作为<strong style="color: blue;">开胃</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">补水</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">解腻</strong>的好选择，不光<strong style="color: blue;">喜庆好看</strong>，<strong style="color: blue;">也承载着<span style="color: green;">诸事顺遂</span>、<span style="color: green;">吉祥如意</span>的美好寓意</strong>。<strong style="color: blue;">过年买水果，<span style="color: green;">6种“吉祥果”不能忘</span>，贵贱都买点，兔年大吉大利</strong>，水果不光能够清口吃，<strong style="color: blue;">做成菜肴上桌，也能让人眼前一亮</strong>。</p>
<h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">一、橙子——称心如意</h1>
<p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">黄色</span>代表权贵</strong>，有<strong style="color: blue;">飞黄腾达</strong>的寓意，<strong style="color: blue;">橙与“成”谐音</strong>，<strong style="color: blue;">寓意“<span style="color: green;">心想事成</span>”、“<span style="color: green;">称心如意</span>”</strong>。</p>
<div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img src="https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-qvj2lq49k0/703c4b8b05a74204868c2652bac12636~noop.image?_iz=58558
</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
